# ── Production (Vercel: support.bugchase.com) ───────────────────────────────
# Optional: override API host (defaults to https://bugchase-server.vercel.app/api).
# VITE_API_URL=https://bugchase-server.vercel.app/api
#
# Google Sign-In (optional). Use the same Web Client ID as server GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID.
# In Google Cloud Console → OAuth client → Authorized JavaScript origins, add:
#   https://support.bugchase.com
# VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=

# ── Local dev ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Leave VITE_API_URL unset — Vite proxies /api → http://localhost:5000
